ygData.messageBody:
WHY can't they just put the new servers UP
already? And cap the Tunare server! And just...FIX IT
ALL!<br><br> ..I can't even login anymore! I'm glad EQ is so
popular but.. I wish it wasn't so...buggy...<br><br> ...I
try to zone, I get disconnected. I am trying to get
in and play for the small amount of time on the
weekends that I CAN play, and it's down! AGAIN!<br><br>
..When will they fix this???<br><br> ~Teppeny<br> Hobbit
Druid of the 15th<br> Souls of Peace<br> Tunare server
